title: Rookie Andrus Peat sprains knee; out a few weeks
text:

NEW ORLEANS -- New Orleans Saints rookie tackle Andrus Peat has an MCL sprain and will miss a few weeks, a league source told WWL-TV Sports Director Doug Mouton.
